{"id": "1502265942082846830", "channel_id": "1475263387553501427", "type": 0, "author_id": "1280181546527096993", "author_name": "fjantsa", "author_bot": false, "content": "## SKeyDB Update\n\n### Awakener Database\n- Added sorting by release date.\n- Added source filters for Permanent Banner, Limited units, Arc 1, and Arc 2.\n- Added a new Overview tab with lore and character stories. More things will be added here later.\n- Moved Enlightens and Talents into the Upgrades tab.\n- Improved character scaling data, numbers, and descriptions.\n- Added the recently added Absolute Axioms to all characters.\n\n### Wheels\n- No major changes.\n- Includes data corrections and improved numbers/descriptions.\n\n### Posses\n- Added a new Posses database.\n- Includes descriptions, obtain sources, lore, and related details.\n- Supports Forbidden Lore scaling through Database settings.\n- Scaling uses your account level and owned Posse collection data.\n\n### Covenants\n- Added a new Covenants database.\n- Includes descriptions, obtain sources, lore, and related details.\n\n### Builder & Collection\n- Added info buttons that open database popups directly on the page for quick reference.\n- Fixed backend collection/builder handling around saved data.\n- Builder import/export should work better again, including in-game lineup codes.\n\n### Heads Up\nThis update includes a lot of backend data changes. Existing collection data should keep working, and automatically migrate to the \"new\" version. If not, I'm very sorry <:dead:1356082627509092372>", "timestamp": "2026-05-08T11:08:31.344000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1475263387553501427", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Complete Team Builder and Unit Database Resource", "forum_channel_id": "1304022827824844842", "thread_tags": ["1448212178447368322", "1448214877096251547", "1304022948000043028"]}
